<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/968988-my-book-stops-at-page-188-then-jumps-to">My book stops at page 188, then jumps to page 45, goes all the way up to page 76 and then jumps to page 221, leaving two whole chapters mostly missing. Having in mind what book this is, it&#39;s hard to tell whether this was done on purpose or if there&#39;s a printing mistake in my copy. I&#39;ve looked online and there&#39;s no mention to this page-jumping business. Is it on purpose or do I have a bad copy?</a>
</div>
