1blog=1v1=19wAAChHalXnXrH7MDypFyg.1"><div data-reactid=".zjg0ahydoi.1:$kca=2//blog/amzn1=1gr=1blog=1v1=19wAAChHalXnXrH7MDypFyg.1.0"><a class="gr-h4 gr-h4--serif newsPreview__newsHeader" href="https://www.goodreads.com/blog/show/1571-the-most-popular-books-about-books-for-avid-readers?ref=book-show" data-reactid=".zjg0ahydoi.1:$kca=2//blog/amzn1=1gr=1blog=1v1=19wAAChHalXnXrH7MDypFyg.1.0.0">The Most Popular Books About Books for Avid Readers</a></div><div class="newsPreview__excerpt" data-reactid=".zjg0ahydoi.1:$kca=2//blog/amzn1=1gr=1blog=1v1=19wAAChHalXnXrH7MDypFyg.1.1">

 
 
Calling all bibliophiles! What better way to celebrate the joy of reading than with a book about, well, books? 

